House\" title=\"Guest House\">Guest House</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Library_Tower\" title=\"Library Tower\">Library Tower</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:50;\">\n<p><b>Terms:</b>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">Direwolf</a></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Engines_of_War\" title=\"Engines of War\">Engines of War</a></i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hound\" title=\"Hound\">Hound</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Old_gods\" title=\"Old gods\">Northern gods</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">Squire</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">Wolf</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>This page uses content from <b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://concord.fandom.com\">Concordances and Characters wiki at Fandom.com</a></b>. The original content was at <b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://concord.wikia.com/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones:_Chapter_9\">A Game of Thrones: Chapter 9</a></b>. The list of authors can be seen in t